# Project Images Placeholder

This directory will contain all project artwork and case study images.

## Expected Files:

- brand-reveal.jpg
- social-campaign.jpg
- fashion-poster.jpg
- vanguard-coffee.jpg
- aura-cosmetics.jpg
- exhibition-poster.jpg
- sonder-logo.jpg
- chronos-logo.jpg
- whiskey-poster.jpg
- bespoke-product.jpg
- corporate-marketing.jpg
- digital-ad.jpg
- eco-box.jpg

## To Add Images:

1. Save your project artwork files to this directory
2. Update the image paths in `src/utils/constants.ts` if needed
3. Ensure all images are optimized for web (max 500KB each)

## Image Specifications:

- Format: JPG/PNG
- Recommended Size: 1200x800px minimum
- Aspect Ratio: 3:2 or 4:3 preferred
